dct_title_s: Topographic map of Yosemite National Park, California
dct_description_sm: from Geological Survey atlas sheets; surveyed between 1893 and 1906; R.B.. Marshall, chief geographer.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Elevations in southwestern quarter are 85 feet too high."
